algorithm: The new algorithm uses the reciprocal of the element-wise maximum of the logarithm of the item size and the inverse of the rest capacities of the bins, multiplied by the item size itself, and returns the calculated scores.
code:
import numpy as np

def score(item, bins):
    log_item = np.log(item)
    inv_rest_cap = 1 / bins
    max_log_inv = np.maximum(log_item, inv_rest_cap)
    scores = item / max_log_inv
    return scores
